channel.title: /#hashmaps revolution#/ Run escape. pvp, all skills
channel.description:
Hey im hashmap.
i am starting a project which is called run escape. my plan is to bring back the runescape we miss.
Important stuff:
base = delta cleaned *no shit in client.java* mysql = no
aims:
1. PvP like real runescape 04/05 2. Quicker specs 3. 100% specs 4. hard money like Runescape 5. membership 100% 6. 100% f2p shops and p2p shops 7. team capes shops 8. 40% - 80% rs spawns 9. 0lD skewl 10. every skill
Its not gonna be a pressured server.
i just need time, and with school i dont have enough.
just gimme time and the project will be well away ;)
/#hashmaps revolution#/
